000E64  1               ;__CRSRRIGHT_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
000E64  1               ;
000E64  1               ; 	MOVE THE CURSOR RIGHT ONE POSITION, INC THE BUFFER POINTER AND SCROLL IF NECESSARY
