000F9F  1  C9 1A                CMP     #>BUFFER        ; NO WAY WE ARE AT START OF BUFFER
000FA1  1  D0 07                BNE     CHKPOS1         ; SO GO ON
000FA3  1  A5 0D                LDA     EDTPOS          ; CHECK LOW BYTE (BUFFER is page-aligned, low byte = $00)
000FA5  1  D0 03                BNE     CHKPOS1         ; IF WE ARE NOT AT TOP, CONTINUE BACKING UP
000FA7  1  4C FB 11             JMP     GOCSR           ; AT BUFFER START, POSITION CURSOR AND RETURN
